# Maintain rules

Update `.cursor/rules/` when you:

- Add a new package, tool, or major pattern
- Change how client and server communicate
- Establish a convention worth repeating

Rules must stay **short** (under ~15 lines each). Edit existing rules instead of adding long new ones. Remove rules that no longer apply.
